Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:03.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,My name is Conan Edogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:08.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,No... My real name is Shin'ichi Kudo, high-school detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,Today, we'll play back the day when I became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}Love lasts forever, riddles are puzzling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}and Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.28,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}Today's episode is my starting point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:23.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}Watch Shin'ichi's deductions carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0080,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:12.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you get serious for a moment, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to detain all of my guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any more time to be part of your fruitless investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim {\i1}was{\i0} a guest invited to your partyâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:29.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,President Yamazaki of Yatsubishi Bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have a little more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suggesting that the one responsible is in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:39.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The door was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer entered from the next window over on the 3rd floor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then left the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:46.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no footprints below the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:50.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which points to the fact that this was an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:54.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense! It's almost 10 meters to the next window!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:55.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping from one to the other is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killer used the edge of the roof to get across to the next window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there would be less than 2 meters left to the veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.60,0:03:04.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the room where Mr. Yamazaki was.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What childish reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did the killer leave then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they could have jumped the 2 meters to the roof edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which only sticks 10 centimeters out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer brought some rope when leaving the next room over,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,affixed it to the veranda, and then later used it to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:29.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then how was the rope removed from the veranda afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's simple, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A stick was tied to one end of the rope and attached to the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It easily came undone when tugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:41.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should find marks from when the rope was affixed to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:48.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was Mr. Yamazaki doing inside a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:52.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, the killer told him to wait there with the door locked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:56.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because he had something important and secret to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your pompous talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:02.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who was it who broke in and killed Mr. Yamazaki, my best friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one person who knows enough of this house's layout
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and who could walk throughout it without raising any suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:11.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,None other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:29.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking! My leg hasn't even healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your leg healed 3 months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your physician has disclosed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We also know that you and your best friend Mr. Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,had under-the-table financial dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really in your debt, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always being there to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into any other difficult cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,feel free to contact me, Detective Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break here, Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:42.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought I'd wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Works better than an alarm clock, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of books you have here never ceases to amaze me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:53.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it {\i1}was{\i0} because of all these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:57.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that your father was able to become an international mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:58.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving around, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:02.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you testing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:06.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell this to anyone, got it?! This is just between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a Personal Mobility Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I perfect it, traffic jams will become a thing of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:15.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be filthy rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these? Oh, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:27.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:34.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That stupid kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cuz he's a high school student playing a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I hardly ever get any jobs anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Shin'ichi is just really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to make a living, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The famous detective Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:56.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The modern-day Japanese Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:59.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Also considered by many as the savior of the Japanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:02.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should write him a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.55,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran Mouri\N2nd year student, Teitan High
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stupid! Grinning like you're some big shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so angry about, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad at all that my dad can't get any work because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my fault your dad doesn't get much work, he's just not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:36.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I told you, I'm not mad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I'd expect from the head of the karate club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't quit the soccer club you would've been a big hero here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only did soccer to acquire the physical prowess that all detectives need!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes had his fencing, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:10.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But those are just novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a detective that everyone's heard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:14.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:18.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always calm and composed no matter the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's practically overflowing with intelligence and refinement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And his keen powers of observation and deduction are unparalleled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:26.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, his violin skills are equal to those of a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:35.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Doyle's Sherlock Holmes is the world's greatest detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:39.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like him so much, why don't you become a writer like your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to write about detectives, I want to BE one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The modern-day Japanese Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:51.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The exhilaration from catching the bad guys is beyond description!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:54.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try being a detective once and there's no going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at all these fan letters! Detectives are popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine that you're always flirting with girls, but at least choose a favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:13.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:17.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing! We better hurry or we'll miss class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:22.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten your promise for tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:31.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said if I won the karate tournament that you'd take me to Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sicko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:09.60,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi Yoshida
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:09.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so totally fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:13.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta Kojima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:13.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko Tsuburaya
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was so totally bad for the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:16.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For a big guy you sure get scared easy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Mystery Coaster should be okay for you two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:23.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, we only have enough left for the train back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:27.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:38.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, Shin'ichi! There's room on the Mystery Coaster! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:44.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tryin' to sneak in for free, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:56.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The coolest thing about Holmes is when he first met his assistant Watson,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:11:02.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he could tell he went to Afghanistan as a military doctor just by shaking his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a gymnastics club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know him, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the blisters on her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:21.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only girls who train on the horizontal bar ever get this many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can get blisters doing tennis too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:29.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I saw earlier when the wind blew her skirt up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:32.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only those with experience on the horizontal bar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:35.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,get marks like that on their thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fair if you knew from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep holding her hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:42.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Quit botherin' my pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:50.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of yours? In that case, why don't we switch places in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:55.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it'd be impolite to disturb Aiko and Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've liked you ever since I wasâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.71,0:12:09.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We can get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:11.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:16.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just get in line for seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way is the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're trying to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:24.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way! We're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:34.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you see? Conan Doyle must have wanted to be like Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.61,0:12:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out with Holmes and Doyle, you big mystery geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:46.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked so forward to coming here with you, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you see the way I feel about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, actually, I feel the sameâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you! What're you so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously just kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't make a good detective if you're tricked so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did look forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:41.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:53.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are police cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't sneak in for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you that high school detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to loiter around because of an ordinary accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us leave already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:21.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! This was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:26.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the culprit was one of the 7 other people on the roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:29.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the truth, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Kudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shin'ichi Kudo, the famous high school student detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Savior of the Japanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:47.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, temporarily taking you and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} out of the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there were 5 passengers total.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:54.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers A and B in the first row were both friends of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:15:00.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C, who was both friend and girlfriend to the victim, was in the third row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.31,0:15:05.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And D and E were the men in black who sat behind the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:09.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone had their safety guards on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:14.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so only the woman sitting next to him could have committed the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:16.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for your little detective games!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:23.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What with this guy's icy stare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:27.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's glaring like he's killed lots of people before without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}W-Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:32.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! There's a knife in this woman's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I've never seen that before in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:40.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiko! And I thought you and Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} were on good terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:40.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious the girl did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take her into custody as the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! T-Then who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:03.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:08.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife was in Aiko's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Severing a person's head with such a knife would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:33.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially for a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:39.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You put the knife in Aiko's purse in advance to put the blame on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:43.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was sitting in the very front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make it impossible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:46.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's entirely possible if she utilized the coaster's speed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:49.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in conjunction with a bit of piano wire or some rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the murderer, and Inspector Megure is the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:59.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, before pulling the safety guard down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:02.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I put a purse-like object behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the guard comes down and... See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With the extra space, it's easy to slip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:14.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I take out a pre-prepared rope with a hook at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:19.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I put my legs around the guard, stretch back, and place the rope loop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,around the victim's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:24.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All while inside a pitch- black tunnel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I attach the hook to the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:29.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After this, the coaster's speed and power willâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:32.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy! What proof do you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:38.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The pearl necklace you were wearing before you got on the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tears served as another clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew beforehand that the victim was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why you silently wept before doing him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:02.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The trails of tears that go horizontally across your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way your tears could have flowed horizontally
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was if you were crying while on the coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his fault, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He forsook me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:20.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi, you were going out with Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Long before I met you two in college!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:30.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I decided to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where we had our very first date, using the necklace he gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't affected one bit, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to crime scenes now.\NYou know, torn up bodies and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to forget about it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These sorta things happen all the time, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:39.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh? It's one of the men in black from the roller coaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ran! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Waitâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:49.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:05.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm not sure why, but I could just tell somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:12.54,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I got the horrible feeling that I'd never see Shin'ichi again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, Company Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late! I've been waiting for two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came alone, just as I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:35.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I rode the roller coaster and checked from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself! The money comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I take it you have no objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whoa! There's at least 100 million in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:46.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This concludes our transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and give me the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The incriminating film that shows your company smuggling weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all of the film, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who in the world are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of your little detective game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just our luck, having this punk kid follow us around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.74,0:21:14.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he that detective, boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:15.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to take care of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:18.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The place is still crawlin' with cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:23.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use this. Our organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't even show up in autopsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:31.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been tested on humans yet, but let's consider this a trial run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:37.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.14,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}M-My body's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's like my bones are melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:01.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:25.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a dead body over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:27.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:31.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Guess I really did die...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.99,0:23:37.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.83,0:23:41.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ah! That poison must not work on humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:44.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand up, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name's Shinâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.62,0:24:05.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.42,0:24:07.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conanâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.86,0:24:14.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Kidnapping of the Company President's Daughter"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:19.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Skyscraper
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:24.59,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.15,0:24:21.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,{\a6}Next time, I'll shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:22.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,{\a6}Not my turn yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.97,0:24:24.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0080,,{\a6}Not even close.
